{"tid":1892421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知大家知唔知，少數派既「敗選聯盟」依家做緊啲咩","createTime":"2020-02-22T13:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T05:06:32.000Z","uid":166588,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69a2104e4a3fffd32b704e650a861ed83bb7f10c","tid":1892421,"uid":166588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%80%A3%E7%B7%9A-101363494770940/?tn-str=k*F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B7%259A-101363494770940%2F%3Ftn-str%3Dk%2AF&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=12b0a7fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%80%A3%E7%B7%9A-101363494770940/?tn-str=k*F</a><br />\n呢個「新界地區抗疫連線」，個專頁入面避開所有同政治黃藍有關既論述，淨係講防疫同派口罩，事實上佢哋係由新界各區既敗選區選員組成，核心係民建聯，牽頭係一啲地區衛星團體。至少證實咗既係大埔區召集人就係黃碧嬌。<br />\n佢哋刻意唔表示自己身份，但凡係呢啲派口罩活動就會露面，然後話成班LOSER喺抗疫前線，又話啲街坊都好唔捨得佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，選舉既反擊戰一早開打咗，大家唔好鬆懈，要支持或者多提點現任既區議員，唔好俾班垃圾有機會捲土重來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de88932c8680855034f8ff40a7e04e16ee77e62a","tid":1892421,"uid":166588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"民建聯老樹盤根咁多年，大量衛星團體依然有強大動員能力，現任區議員唔好好累積番好既政績，幾年後就會翻盤，慎之！"},{"pid":"491e5f925e28ef0ea75251c776dc3e21d75482f1","tid":1892421,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"係 班柒頭輸咗但賴死唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n霸住個辦事處繼續蛇齋餅儍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4f8960c7c9b17a5701c5ad1ff266ca2b1dbbaa","tid":1892421,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2